.org/10.5281/zenodo.6404842" figureDoi-2="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6404844" figureDoi-3="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6404846" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/6404836/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/6404842/files/figure.png" httpUri-2="https://zenodo.org/record/6404844/files/figure.png" httpUri-3="https://zenodo.org/record/6404846/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">Figures 1–4</figureCitation>
